{"tid":122030,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"點解Adv/Galgame改篇動畫易令人失望","createTime":"2017-02-15T16:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T07:40:58.000Z","uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f5273901277f89891a8e94282c0f2338e0199cc","tid":122030,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:49:21.000Z","msg":"雖然成功例子都唔少,但係好似唔少GALGAME改篇動畫都令人失望,近年既例子都唔少<br />\n甚至有啲比喻為爛到世界級,但係唔少人話原作神級<br />\n<br />\n係因為文字類遊戲內心獨白多動畫難演繹出黎<br />\n定係情節腦補場景多同動畫做出黎差別大有失落感<br />\n定係亂改劇情搞到爛<br />\n定係遊戲入面要體驗唔同分支先了解到套作品,但係動畫唔夠時間做<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032079c59a9e61cf1b86cec95692846ea16643ec","tid":122030,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:53:06.000Z","msg":"因為冇＄<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"9af3b51987bd077ad535e72205aa9532dc1b16df","tid":122030,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為冇＄<br />\n<br />\n完</blockquote><br />\n秒!"},{"pid":"0fb2179556de5be7971309ed95bdf327594dc1f7","tid":122030,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:55:06.000Z","msg":"成功例子不得不提灰色的果實系列<br />\n<br />\n用盡心機重現曬個故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0989c681c153c8a33985f22c0b8b339cebb857","tid":122030,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:55:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為冇＄<br />\n<br />\n完</blockquote><br />\n即係gal改動畫嘅budget比輕小說改動畫嘅budget低？"},{"pid":"aa3311b976e2e053ae0195011667a7b08147fbb6","tid":122030,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:56:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成功例子不得不提灰色的果實系列<br />\n<br />\n用盡心機重現曬個故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但大多數gal動畫化都係失敗收場"},{"pid":"cfec01a1f7fc82e14e06d9ece02879336c475b79","tid":122030,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:57:42.000Z","msg":"漫改其實係咪比其他改篇易啲<br />\n有哂分鏡,連載漫畫又係一排更一次,有個劇情架構一集講啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cae777ab351876ecd42d25177975e694ce3a373","tid":122030,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:59:11.000Z","msg":"志倉千代丸咁多套adv好似得s;g係改得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32b706ff1e3c8ca04ada79f1de155a050044a99","tid":122030,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:00:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>漫改其實係咪比其他改篇易啲<br />\n有哂分鏡,連載漫畫又係一排更一次,有個劇情架構一集講啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都想知gal改對比漫改輕改原創真係質素比較差？"},{"pid":"ab1533d94f1da174fd8a2f2841490fd9baec513e","tid":122030,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:00:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成功例子不得不提灰色的果實系列<br />\n<br />\n用盡心機重現曬個故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但大多數gal動畫化都係失敗收場</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講黎講去真正大失敗既有幾多套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n動畫化一定要修改些少劇情架啦<br />\n原作廚又會走出黎鬧<br />\n比你衰極最近講rewrite好未<br />\n依家都仲行緊season2希望救翻小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066536a118801acc7345f9cc3f0f00c4f54b577f","tid":122030,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:02:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為冇＄<br />\n<br />\n完</blockquote><br />\n即係gal改動畫嘅budget比輕小說改動畫嘅budget低？</blockquote><br />\nGal本身劇本好長+好多重要野分散哂係唔同支線度<br />\n例如fate都3條線<br />\n但唔係套套都fate咁大把錢逐條黎<br />\n夾硬將唔同線既炒埋一碟<br />\n有時比足你24集都唔掂<br />\n但又冇錢唔可以學fate咁逐條拍"},{"pid":"333be6db12d7152537880c107f4e6a848f0c5e72","tid":122030,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:09:32.000Z","msg":"不過唔驚<br />\n而家D人識玩先課金後出貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遊戲社有錢就夠牙力同制作組bargain<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0033f717b506301e385529f887d0ceee8f59ade2","tid":122030,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:12:09.000Z","msg":"會唔會因爲好多gal 重點係18+<br />\n但係動畫做唔到，所以俾人負皮<br />\n若果隻gal本身賣點唔係18+，例如fate賣世界觀同設定，咁動畫化會比較容易成功？"},{"pid":"d546fc7bd0cd3827847451df285064f0de3e29bf","tid":122030,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:20:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會因爲好多gal 重點係18+<br />\n但係動畫做唔到，所以俾人負皮<br />\n若果隻gal本身賣點唔係18+，例如fate賣世界觀同設定，咁動畫化會比較容易成功？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7133d235e7b491d0c7a903abd42e5479bc1b78f3","tid":122030,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:28:36.000Z","msg":"賣世界觀同設定，咁動畫化會比較容易成功...<br />\n我都想, 承你貴言<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42bd00c7341d61828c778abd3e8586c347b6109","tid":122030,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:30:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賣世界觀同設定，咁動畫化會比較容易成功...<br />\n我都想, 承你貴言<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nChing等緊邊套"},{"pid":"bada17753f8a75c8b4c5960b48fc7c7f186c124f","tid":122030,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:31:11.000Z","msg":"都要有廚鍾意揸住本設定集打飛機先得架"},{"pid":"a1e7c90834837cf9fec5304a56e2dded531cf2f5","tid":122030,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:31:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>賣世界觀同設定，咁動畫化會比較容易成功...<br />\n我都想, 承你貴言<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nChing等緊邊套</blockquote><br />\nChaos hea