e>會唔會因爲好多gal 重點係18+<br />\n但係動畫做唔到，所以俾人負皮<br />\n若果隻gal本身賣點唔係18+，例如fate賣世界觀同設定，咁動畫化會比較容易成功？</blockquote><br />\n唔計18+ 有d劇本本身只係design for game <br />\n改動畫就要由頭寫過 翻手寫又未必有原作寫得咁好<br />\n好似E17你點改<br />\n<br />\n更加唔好講 遊戲性更重 D視點跳來跳去 ge R11</blockquote><br />\nE17果種靠玩家既觀察盲點既<br />\n冇咩可能出動畫架啦<br />\n<br />\n而家剩係等Island睇佢會點做<br />\n玩game我俾佢由頭呃到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nN個twistsN個伏筆我基本上一個都估唔到<br />\n唯一一個估到既都唔係睇劇情估到<br />\n係玩倦左去睇番玩左既CG先留意到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nC;C我反而仲估中唔少<br />\n<br />\n佢今個月出PSV版賺埋最後一水<br />\n希望出佢2季啦<br />\n同埋係動畫補完同再講清楚D未講清既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e061e2755771ec2025fa036607904b02e518dda8","tid":122030,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:52:24.000Z","msg":"呢篇鬼佬評Island唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://vnrw.wordpress.com/2016/05/19/vn-island/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvnrw.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2F19%2Fvn-island%2F&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=39b43f20\" target=\"_blank\">https://vnrw.wordpress.com/2016/05/19/vn-island/</a><br />\n佢話係佢10年後4隻神作之一: 穢翼/WA2/櫻の詩/Island<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIsland is so far only the fourth game since 2010 that I can think of as possessing the qualities to constitute a &ldquo;kamige&rdquo;, the others being Sakura no Uta, While Album 2, and Aiyoku no Eustia. And while I admit Sakura no Uta is probably the most profound of the group, Island is sure the one I had the most fun with."},{"pid":"b506c7761d0fe1f0e09f71acc77e21a1bf12a9fe","tid":122030,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:55:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢篇鬼佬評Island唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://vnrw.wordpress.com/2016/05/19/vn-island/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvnrw.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2F19%2Fvn-island%2F&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=39b43f20\" target=\"_blank\">https://vnrw.wordpress.com/2016/05/19/vn-island/</a><br />\n佢話係佢10年後4隻神作之一: 穢翼/WA2/櫻の詩/Island<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIsland is so far only the fourth game since 2010 that I can think of as possessing the qualities to constitute a &ldquo;kamige&rdquo;, the others being Sakura no Uta, While Album 2, and Aiyoku no Eustia. And while I admit Sakura no Uta is probably the most profound of the group, Island is sure the one I had the most fun with.</blockquote><br />\n4隻最好動畫化既穢翼唔做<br />\n反而Island會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔知會點了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4f70a75e2c8d6b0de5e807c3a4c4fc0d4325e8","tid":122030,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:20:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想睇素晴日動畫化</blockquote><br />\n唔好講唔知點拍<br />\n問題係冇人想聽哲學講座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343dcfb49b31661aa8d0ba205fe11585831e0ab9","tid":122030,"uid":28956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:32:05.000Z","msg":"我同件鬼佬口味都差幾遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e67ae4b4bade93330095d212ca40459bc17b4a","tid":122030,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T06:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢篇鬼佬評Island唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://vnrw.wordpress.com/2016/05/19/vn-island/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvnrw.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2F19%2Fvn-island%2F&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=39b43f20\" target=\"_blank\">https://vnrw.wordpress.com/2016/05/19/vn-island/